metadata.name: NYMPHOMANIAC
metadata.description:
She enjoyed the longer rights than days, 
Her quest for happiness carried her to new places.  
Places that dubbed her a Nymphomaniac, 
And offered her different dimensions!  
She went off on a tangent 
As if there was no tomorrow.  
Leaving pieces of herself in every man 
She got intimate with.  
Her agony yearned for  yearned for pleasure,  
leading her to move 
From place to place, 
From individual to individual!  
With an insatiable sexual appetite!   

Medium :Hand drawn Charcoal on paper
